      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to prohibit the Administrator of General Services from establishing per diem reimbursements rates for travel within the continental United States (commonly known as "CONUS") for certain fiscal years below a certain level, and for other purposes.</title>
